latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Wow, its been more than five years ! Stumbled upon this monologue that I shot while I was training to become an actor 😊
It's so important to look back and see how far we have come. It's an appreciation post for sure as joining @jeffgoldbergstudio was one of the best decisions of my life as this is where I learnt that acting is all about being truthful and in the moment. That characters should be studied well before reaching the set so that we can slip easily into the deeper layers of the parts we play and most importantly I learnt  that it's all about the choices you make between 'action' and 'cut'. So grateful for the change in my thought process after training. A life decision I am proud of ❤️ Some firsts are always special 😍

Had the best time shooting for this gorgeous property being a travel lover ❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Get rid of patchy/bumpy Chicken skin.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys ! 
Been really wanting to do this for a while since you all have always been showing so much love and appreciation. So in return, I promise to talk more about Fashion - Fitness - Beauty  and help you guys become your  gorgeous best self.
Chose to make a video on this issue , that most of my girl friends have faced and I have dealt with for years . Chicken Skin or Keratosis Pilaris !! A common skin condition in which there is a build up of keratin - hair protein around the  hair follicle , making it appear like small bumps. I have shared with you all a couple of easy home care and remedies to take care of the issue and help you get smooth skin . Comment below and let me know if you like it ❤️ #skin #beauty #beautyvlog #influencer #skincare #homemaderemedies #loveyourskin

latestIgtvVideos.title: Dromen & Co Vacay kit review
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ok ! So this is a very useful vacay kit for all the girls who are constantly on the run. Now you can achieve the perfect sunkissed look with the help of just a pink blush and a highlighter where ever you are.
You also get blotting paper sheets to remove the excess oil and dirt from the surface of your skin and makeup removal sheets to remove the make up later. Easy to carry-useful-worth it.
